item.title: Where Will Opendoor Stock Be in 5 Years?
item.description: Opendoor Technologies (NASDAQ: OPEN) saw its stock nearly 10x after Reddit crowned it "the next Carvana." But with crumbling fundamentals, negative earnings, and slashed guidance, this may be more hype than turnaround. Should investors hold, sell, or double down?
